Bradley Lee WINTERS, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES. No. 13-6113. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 15, 2013. Case below, 716 F.3d 1098 . Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit denied. Justice KAGAN took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
